Class FSlistFileElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.FSlistFileElement

  • public class FSlistFileElement
extends java.lang.Object
    This Class host the FileElement wich the list is composed, handle some control/filter when an item is added and set the type of mode of the list

    Meschio
